  <h2 class="sh">AI ethics for everyone ⚖️</h2>
  <p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--k3);margin-bottom:1.5rem;line-height:1.75">AI is powerful. With great toast comes great responsibility.</p>
  <div class="egrid" style="margin-bottom:1rem">
    <div class="ec g"><div class="eclbl">✅ Do this</div><div class="ectxt">Use AI to <strong>help you learn</strong> — ask it to explain, then put the answer in your own words.</div></div>
    <div class="ec b"><div class="eclbl">❌ Not this</div><div class="ectxt">Copy AI answers word for word as your own work. That's not learning — it's letting a machine think for you.</div></div>
    <div class="ec g"><div class="eclbl">✅ Do this</div><div class="ectxt"><strong>Double-check important facts.</strong> AI makes stuff up. For health, legal, or money decisions — always talk to a real professional too.</div></div>
    <div class="ec b"><div class="eclbl">❌ Not this</div><div class="ectxt">Trust AI blindly on things that really matter. "The AI said so" is not good enough for serious life decisions.</div></div>
    <div class="ec g"><div class="eclbl">✅ Do this</div><div class="ectxt">Keep <strong>private info private.</strong> Your name, address, phone, passwords — never share these with any AI chatbot, ever.</div></div>
    <div class="ec b"><div class="eclbl">❌ Not this</div><div class="ectxt">Share sensitive info in AI chats. Those conversations can be stored and used to train future models.</div></div>
    <div class="ec g"><div class="eclbl">✅ Do this</div><div class="ectxt">Use AI to <strong>lift people up</strong> — write kind messages, make information accessible, help someone who is struggling.</div></div>
    <div class="ec b"><div class="eclbl">❌ Not this</div><div class="ectxt">Use AI to spread fake information, create deceptive content, or generate anything that hurts real people.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="psec">💬 Ethics prompts to think with</div>
